@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yokugy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    v1 = 0.68
    v1 = ((v1 - (tmp + 0.93 - v2 + 0.41)) / tmp)
    v0 = (0.56 + wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.16)))
    tmp = (v0 / ((v0 + 0.98 - tmp + 0.67) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.11)))
    v1 = wp.abs((v1 - 0.84))
    data[tid] = v0
